const customSizeCode = ` .customSize { .reactify-ui-tooltip__bubble { font-size: 30px; } } Hover over me to show small tooltip Hover over me to show medium tooltip Hover over me to show large tooltip Hover over me to show custom size tooltip `; const simpleCode = 'Hover over me to show tooltip'; const positionCode = ` Hover over me to show top tooltip Hover over me to show left tooltip Hover over me to show right tooltip Hover over me to show bottom tooltip `; const themesCode = ` Hover over me to show primary tooltip
Hover over me to show secondary tooltip
Hover over me to show dark tooltip
Hover over me to show light tooltip
Hover over me to show info tooltip
Hover over me to show warning tooltip
Hover over me to show danger tooltip
Hover over me to show success tooltip `; export { customSizeCode, positionCode, simpleCode, themesCode, };
